General.Name: Scout Gaming Group AB
General.Description: Scout Gaming Group AB (publ) provides B2B daily fantasy, sportsbook, fantasy betting, and other sports betting products primarily in Sweden, Norway, Ukraine, and Malta. It offers a network based fantasy sports solution with support for various sports and leagues through an in-house StatCenter, which provides real-time information to players. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
